articles.author: Mark Schlabach
articles.title: Ohio St., IU, Texas A&M, Alabama top CFP ranking - ESPN
articles.description: The top five teams remained unchanged in the second set of rankings released by the College Football Playoff selection committee on Tuesday, with Ohio State at No. 1, followed by fellow unbeatens Indiana and Texas A&M, and one-loss Alabama and Georgia.
